Super excited to share key stats of the first week of XMRec #WSDM2022 Cup:
 - 79 registered participants,
 - 14 active teams,
 - 56 submissions.
 - Highest nDCG@10: 0.6215 (compared to last week's 0.5025!)

Many thanks to the participants, and look forward to more submissions! https://t.co/Fnq9H9JsLb
